<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cadastro na Loja WR25</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #555;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Cadastro na Loja WR25</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Olá, ${nome}!</p>
            <p>${mensagem}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Em caso de dúvidas, entre em contato conosco.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>